(602, 'zakku', 'Elevated Push-Ups', 'Place hands on a box or bench shoulder-width apart and feet on the ground behind you in a plank position. Lower your chest towards the box by bending your elbows, then push back up to the starting position.', 'eximg/Elevated Push-Ups.gif', 'Beginner', 'Chest'),
