(132, 'joker', '5', 'Butt Kicks', ' Stand with your feet hip-width apart. Jog in place while kicking your heels up towards your glutes with each step. Aim to make contact with your glutes with each heel kick.', 'eximg/Butt Kicks.gif', 'Beginner', '2024-09-28 14:44:57', 'Warm Up', '3 sets, 60 seconds each set'),
