(137, 'joker', '6', 'Step-Up', 'Stand in front of a low step or bench. Step one foot onto the step, pressing through your heel to lift your body up onto the step, then step back down and repeat on the other side.', 'eximg/Step-Up.gif', 'Beginner', '2024-09-28 14:44:57', 'Legs', '3 sets of 10-12 reps (per leg)'),
(138, 'joker', '6', 'Cat-Cow Stretch', 'Start on your hands and knees in a tabletop position, with your wrists under your shoulders and knees under your hips. Inhale as you arch your back, lifting your chest and tailbone towards the ceiling (Cow Pose). Exhale as you round your back, tucking your chin to your chest and drawing your belly button towards your spine (Cat Pose). Repeat the sequence, flowing smoothly between the two poses.', 'eximg/Cat-Cow Stretch.gif', 'Beginner', '2024-09-28 14:44:57', 'Back', '3 sets, 8-10 reps'),
(139, 'joker', '6', 'Towel Curls', 'Sit on the ground with your legs extended and place a towel under one foot. Grip the ends of the towel with both hands and perform bicep curls by pulling the towel towards your shoulders.', 'eximg/Towel Curls.gif', 'Beginner', '2024-09-28 14:44:57', 'Arms', '3 sets of 15-20 reps'),
