(463, 'alone', '4', 'Banded Squats', 'Stand on the center of the resistance band with feet shoulder-width apart. Hold the handles or ends of the band at shoulder height, palms facing inward. Perform squats by pushing your hips back and bending your knees while keeping tension on the band.', 'eximg/Banded squat.gif', 'Beginner', '2024-09-28 15:25:41', 'Legs', '3 sets of 15-20 reps'),
