(677, 'lov', '1', 'Reverse Flyes', 'Stand with a dumbbell in each hand, feet shoulder-width apart. Bend your knees slightly and hinge forward at your hips, keeping your back flat. With a slight bend in your elbows, raise your arms out to the sides until they are parallel to the floor, squeezing your shoulder blades together, then lower back down.', 'eximg/Reverse Flyes.gif', 'Beginner', '2024-09-29 04:03:17', 'Back', '3 sets, 8-10 reps'),
